{
  "stem": "11771.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I was a afraid to knock on the door or to not to knock on the door.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Eventually, I figure I don't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Where ?] I was going, my plan was to go back to Juzia, to the same Polish girl.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And I am afraid to ask, but I start to figure out when my conscience came back where I run-- run always here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I ran away from here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Juzia is here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She is between [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when I figure it out, when I start to go the other direction, I figured I'd find her somehow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I'm going, and I'm going, and I'm going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So all night, my luck was, it was always a little raining-- cold rain on my body.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I took off the sack because it was bothering me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was rubbing me on my body.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It  was hurting me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Instead to protect me, it was making me more-- the wounds open.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the boots also, they opened up the wounds that I got from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They opened it up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it was leaking blood.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was bothering me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I complete naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Eventually, my sense of directions didn't help me to go to Juzia-- the same place where I ran away in the first place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was early in morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was going all night in circles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I find out I am in the wrong direction, I go back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But eventually, I find it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With the sense of the directions, believe it or not, the dogs were barking by a farmer, they were giving me the signs where I am and what direction should I go.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
